	Dr Victor Rulev is an author of 92 publicatons in the sphere of Gynecological Endocrinology, Reproductive Gynecology, co-author of two patents for inventions in Gynecological Endocrinology.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	For more than 25 years (since 1992) he has been an Obstetrician-Gynecologist of the highest category.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	Dr Rulev is a highly qualified specialist in Reproductive Gynecology and Gynecological Endocrinology, in treatment of all types of female infertility, general gynecologic conditions including external genital endometriosis, polycystic ovarian syndrome, recurrent miscarriages, ectopic pregnancies, chronic and acute pelvic inflammatory diseases in women, menstrual cycle disorders, endometrial hyperplastic processes, ovarian cysts, uterine fibroids, chronic pelvic pains, perimenopausal disorders, juvenile bleeding, etc.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	Since 1991, Dr Rulev has been performing gynecological laparo-hysteroscopies, the technique learned by him not only in Russia but also from well-known foreign specailists in Germany and France. Totally, over 10,000 diagnostoc laparoscopies have been performed by Dr Rulev.
&lt;/p&gt;";s:18:"~UF_DESCRIPTION_EN";s:1138:"<p>
	Dr Victor Rulev is an author of 92 publicatons in the sphere of Gynecological Endocrinology, Reproductive Gynecology, co-author of two patents for inventions in Gynecological Endocrinology.
</p>
<p>
	For more than 25 years (since 1992) he has been an Obstetrician-Gynecologist of the highest category.
</p>
<p>
	Dr Rulev is a highly qualified specialist in Reproductive Gynecology and Gynecological Endocrinology, in treatment of all types of female infertility, general gynecologic conditions including external genital endometriosis, polycystic ovarian syndrome, recurrent miscarriages, ectopic pregnancies, chronic and acute pelvic inflammatory diseases in women, menstrual cycle disorders, endometrial hyperplastic processes, ovarian cysts, uterine fibroids, chronic pelvic pains, perimenopausal disorders, juvenile bleeding, etc.
</p>
